8px" data-srcset="https://thediplomat.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/sizes/td-list-xs-1/thediplomat_2024-04-22-203159.jpg 58w, https://thediplomat.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/sizes/td-list-xs-2/thediplomat_2024-04-22-203159.jpg 116w" data-src="https://thediplomat.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/sizes/td-list-xs-1/thediplomat_2024-04-22-203159.jpg" src="https://thediplomat.com/wp-content/themes/td_theme_v3/assets/img-paceholder_square.gif"></figure><h5>Security</h5><h4>RIP, SSF: Unpacking the PLA’s Latest Restructuring</h4></a></div><div class="swiper-slide"><a href="/2024/04/reconceptualizing-asias-security-challenges/" class="td-post"><figure class="td-img td-post__img"><img class="swiper-lazy" alt="Reconcept&amp;shy;ualizing Asia&rsquo;s Security Challenges" title="Reconcept&amp;shy;ualizing Asia&rsquo;s Security Challenges" sizes="58px" data-srcset="https://thediplomat.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/sizes/td-list-xs-1/thediplomat_2024-04-19-195303.jpg 58w, https://thediplomat.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/sizes/td-list-xs-2/thediplomat_2024-04-19-195303.jpg 116w" data-src="https://thediplomat.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/sizes/td-list-xs-1/thediplomat_2024-04-19-195303.jpg" src="https://thediplomat.com/wp-content/themes/td_theme_v3/assets/img-paceholder_square.gif"></figure><h5>Security</h5><h4>Reconcept&shy;ualizing Asia’s Security Challenges</h4></a></div><div class="swiper-slide"><a href="/2024/04/comparing-gray-zone-tactics-in-the-red-sea-and-the-south-china-sea/" class="td-post"><figure class="td-img td-post__img"><img class="swiper-lazy" alt="Comparing Gray-Zone Tactics in the Red Sea and the South China Sea" title="Comparing Gray-Zone Tactics in the Red Sea and the South China Sea" sizes="58px" data-srcset="https://thediplomat.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/sizes/td-list-xs-1/thediplomat_2024-04-19-133508.jpg 58w, https://thediplomat.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/sizes/td-list-xs-2/thediplomat_2024-04-19-133508.jpg 116w" data-src="https://thediplomat.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/sizes/td-list-xs-1/thediplomat_2024-04-19-133508.jpg" src="https://thediplomat.com/wp-content/themes/td_theme_v3/assets/img-paceholder_square.gif"></figure><h5>Security</h5><h4>Comparing Gray-Zone Tactics in the Red Sea and the South China Sea</h4></a></div><div class="swiper-slide"><a href="/2024/04/the-trouble-with-micronesias-new-china-policy/" class="td-post"><figure class="td-img td-post__img"><img class="swiper-lazy" alt="The Trouble With Micronesia&rsquo;s New China Policy" title="The Trouble With Micronesia&rsquo;s New China Policy" sizes="58px" data-srcset="https://thediplomat.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/sizes/td-list-xs-1/thediplomat_2024-04-19-141516.jpg 58w, https://thediplomat.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/sizes/td-list-xs-2/thediplomat_2024-04-19-141516.jpg 116w" data-src="https://thediplomat.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/sizes/td-list-xs-1/thediplomat_2024-04-19-141516.jpg" src="https://thediplomat.com/wp-content/themes/td_theme_v3/assets/img-paceholder_square.gif"></figure><h5>Diplomacy</h5><h4>The Trouble With Micronesia’s New China Policy</h4></a></div><div class="swiper-slide"><a href="/2024/04/the-dire-state-of-womens-rights-in-north-korea/" class="td-post"><figure class="td-img td-post__img"><img class="swiper-lazy" alt="The Dire State of Women&rsquo;s Rights in North Korea" title="The Dire State of Women&rsquo;s Rights in North Korea" sizes="58px" data-srcset="https://thediplomat.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/sizes/td-list-xs-1/thediplomat_2024-04-17-135959.jpg 58w, https://thediplomat.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/sizes/td-list-xs-2/thediplomat_2024-04-17-135959.jpg 116w" data-src="https://thediplomat.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/sizes/td-list-xs-1/thediplomat_2024-04-17-135959.jpg" src="https://thediplomat.com/wp-content/themes/td_theme_v3/assets/img-paceholder_square.gif"></figure><h5>Society</h5><h4>The Dire State of Women’s Rights in North Korea</h4></a></div><div class="swiper-slide"><a href="/2024/04/the-consequences-of-chinas-voracious-appetite-for-illicit-south-african-abalone/" class="td-post"><figure class="td-img td-post__img"><img class="swiper-lazy" alt="The Consequences of China&rsquo;s Voracious Appetite for Illicit South African Abalone&nbsp;" title="The Consequences of China&rsquo;s Voracious Appetite for Illicit South African Abalone&nbsp;" sizes="58px" data-srcset="https://thediplomat.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/sizes/td-list-xs-1/thediplomat_2024-04-17-122327.jpg 58w, https://thediplomat.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/sizes/td-list-xs-2/thediplomat_2024-04-17-122327.jpg 116w" data-src="https://thediplomat.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/sizes/td-list-xs-1/thediplomat_2024-04-17-122327.jpg" src="https://thediplomat.com/wp-content/themes/td_theme_v3/assets/img-paceholder_square.gif"></figure><h5>Environment</h5><h4>The Consequences of China’s Voracious Appetite for Illicit South African Abalone </h4></a></div><div class="swiper-slide"><a href="/2024/04/how-the-sewol-sinking-changed-south-korea/" class="td-post"><figure class="td-img td-post__img"><img class="swiper-lazy" alt="How the Sewol Sinking Changed South Korea" title="How the Sewol Sinking Changed South Korea" sizes="58px" data-srcset="https://thediplomat.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/sizes/td-list-xs-1/thediplomat_2024-04-15-163523.jpg 58w, https://thediplomat.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/sizes/td-list-xs-2/thediplomat_2024-04-15-163523.jpg 116w" data-src="https://thediplomat.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/sizes/td-list-xs-1/thediplomat_2024-04-15-163523.jpg" src="https://thediplomat.com/wp-content/themes/td_theme_v3/assets/img-paceholder_square.gif"></figure><h5>Society</h5><h4>How the Sewol Sinking Changed South Korea</h4></a></div><div class="swiper-slide"><a href="/2024/04/2-years-on-ukraines-sinking-of-the-moskva-intrigues-chinas-naval-strategists/" class="td-post"><figure class="td-img td-post__img"><img class="swiper-lazy" alt="2 Years on, Ukraine&rsquo;s Sinking of the Moskva