<li>&#8220;<a href="https://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-china-55794071">&#8216;Their goal is to destroy everyone&#8217;: Uighur camp detainees allege systematic rape</a>,&#8221; by Matthew Hill, David Campanale, and Joel Gunte for BBC News</li>
