<li>&#8220;<a href="https://www.afp.com/en/inside-chinas-internment-camps-tear-gas-tasers-and-textbooks">Inside China’s internment camps: Tear gas, Tasers and textbooks</a>,&#8221; by Ben Dooley for AFP</li>
</ul>
</div>
		
		
	</aside>
