ctured outrage.</div></a><div class="td-vertical-line td-1"></div><div class="td-vertical-line td-2"></div><div class="td-vertical-line td-3"></div></div></div><div class="td-box td-1"><header><h3>Most Read</h3></header><div class="td-posts td-posts--col"><!-- flag=cache key=td:posts:flag:flag_popular --><a href="/2024/04/the-sexual-revolution-behind-chinas-demographic-crisis/" class="td-post d-1"><figure class="td-img td-post__img td-post__img--right-s"><img alt="The Sexual Revolution Behind China&rsquo;s Demographic Crisis" title="The Sexual Revolution Behind China&rsquo;s Demographic Crisis" sizes="(max-width: 319px) 100vw, (max-width: 752px) 138px, 219px" srcset="https://thediplomat.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/sizes/thumbnail/thediplomat_2022-04-22-144618.jpg 138w, https://thediplomat.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/sizes/td-list-s-2/thediplomat_2022-04-22-144618.jpg 276w, https://thediplomat.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/sizes/td-list-m-1/thediplomat_2022-04-22-144618.jpg 219w, https://thediplomat.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/sizes/td-list-m-2/thediplomat_2022-04-22-144618.jpg 438w" src="https://thediplomat.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/sizes/thumbnail/thediplomat_2022-04-22-144618.jpg" loading="lazy"></figure><h4>The Sexual Revolution Behind China’s Demographic Crisis</h4><h6>By <span>Gabriele Manca</span></h6><div>The “one-child policy” didn’t just artificially limit births; it dramatically reshaped the way Chinese society – particularly women – thinks about sex.</div></a><a href="/2024/04/welcome-to-world-war-iii/" class="td-post d-2"><figure class="td-img td-post__img td-post__img--right-s"><img alt="Welcome to World War III" title="Welcome to World War III" sizes="(max-width: 319px) 100vw, (max-width: 752px) 138px, 219px" srcset="https://thediplomat.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/sizes/thumbnail/thediplomat_2024-04-22-080506.jpg 138w, https://thediplomat.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/sizes/td-list-s-2/thediplomat_2024-04-22-080506.jpg 276w, https://